Observation:Preprocessing improves dataset quality, reduces noise, and makes it suitable for ML modeling.

7. Conclusion

The project successfully develops an **original preprocessing pipeline** for HRV medical sensor data. By improving missing value handling, outlier detection, scaling, and noise reduction, the dataset is more robust and ready for downstream machine learning applications. The pipeline can be adapted to other medical sensor datasets for general applicability.



